steps.observation: who won the 2025 France Tennis Open?

content.text: The 2025 French Open men's singles title was won by Carlos Alcaraz, who defeated Jannik Sinner in the final. In the women's singles, Coco Gauff won her first French Open title by defeating Aryna Sabalenka.
